00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:42.520
Bibi, semuanya akan
baik-baik saja kan?

00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:44.840
Sayang, tetap tenang.

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:46.840
Jangan khawatir.
